Name:Flute Player
Desc:Every night, the Flute Player wakes up and enchants two other players. After the Flute player goes back to sleep, all enchanted players wake up together so they can determine who is and isn't enchanted. The Flute Player wins when all players are enchanted or dead. The Flute Player cannot enchant themselves.
Card:Every night, the Flute Player may enchant two other players. Afterward, all enchanted players wake up together so they can determine who is enchanted. The Flute Player wins when all players are enchanted or dead.
